{"type": "article", "id": 27185, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-23T06:53:24Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27564, "name": "Peleg Design"}, {"id": 27978, "name": "SHareStudios"}, {"id": 27979, "name": "PearsonLloyd"}, {"id": 27980, "name": "Furbo"}, {"id": 27981, "name": "Tomofun"}, {"id": 27982, "name": "Stephanie Hare"}, {"id": 27983, "name": "Axel Brechensbauer"}, {"id": 27984, "name": "Geerke Sticker"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702150557MzVj5b2qpkhoR4IL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Bookmark by Peleg Design</h2>\n<p>一个制作精美的书签可以给阅读体验增加不少乐趣，Peleg Design 就推出了两款动物书签。它们的下半部分与普通的书签无异，上半部分则特意做成突起，这样一来河马和鳄鱼看上去就好像潜在水下只露出脑袋一样。你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01BKJ11SY/\">链接</a>购买到这款可爱的书签。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021110375JcpMFm8xXZdHVaf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63522885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111037xkIXSYC6TvfLD2bF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63522885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111038SJgWGjBaM3PrbVoQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63522885\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111038X9gzJocxpihdTY46.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111039e3KfM1nBAvHlsaNx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111039csCADZegvNMVRj0U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62274619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Vessel lamps by SHareStudios</h2>\n<p>台灯除了照明还能用来做什么？SHare Studios 的设计师 Stephanie Hare 大胆地将玻璃器皿作为底座，搭配手工制作的纸质灯罩，推出了一系列极简风格的灯具。如果不用做花器，只是单纯放上一束花或是一些绿叶也能使人眼前一亮。这里是它的<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/SHareStudios\">购买链接</a>，价格根据大小从 150 到 250 美元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111040pt7zsvSEDHBoelLy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111040h0PIc3CqewnK14Ar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111041txYVgUQS4C7sFEnX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8668516\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111041IAOeX6biTBzoGDvJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66990291\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111042VluOSaZtervWLMmo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111042Q7rImjcPwu2FAiVs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Stack by PearsonLloyd</h2>\n<p>很多人已经有了垃圾分类的意识，外出时会根据垃圾桶的标签进行丢弃，伦敦设计工作室 <a href=\"http://pearsonlloyd.com/\">PearsonLloyd</a> 打算让你在家里也能做到这一点：工作室为厨具品牌 Joseph Joseph 设计的 Stack 是一套分类垃圾箱，由多个塑料垃圾箱构成，采用直立堆叠的方式节省了空间。每个垃圾箱上都有一个带凹槽的滑盖，可以在凹槽上放置标签来区别每个垃圾桶的“职责”。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.josephjoseph.com/en-rw/stack-recycling-separation-bins\">购买链接</a>，根据容量的不同，价格为 50 到 100 英镑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111043pxtBvzsUIkA8bf51.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111043Ttv9g4FjJWL657RH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111044Bl02Chiq9GJdz7UW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111044wRtIDCumdy5FkiWX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111044rGfPpc5BTUzDWKym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Fish Pocket Knife by Axel Brechensbauer</h2>\n<p>这一系列外形可爱的小鱼刀由设计师 Axel Brechensbauer 为 Areaware 设计，其中“鱼身”是由山毛榉制成的刀柄，刀片可以通过设计成鱼鳍的拉钩取出，“鱼尾”则是一个开瓶器。三条“小鱼”成套出售的价格为 65 美元，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.areaware.com/collections/bundles/products/fish-pocket-knife-bundle\">链接</a>购买。试想一下，当你和朋友在公园野餐，你从口袋中掏出一条“小鱼”，用它轻松地开启一罐啤酒或是切开一个水果，会是多么吸引眼球的一件事。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111045iJICv6bqVhTrM4Y7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111046svo0W4gMdRIUxnTm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111046LjaN3H7FQkPAnB6K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111047mWlUA6rnf0MYcjIG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021110475wKrBy3zZMR7TLik.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111048HtgiCWoAbVj4Ty2e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Concrete cat/dog bed by Geerke Sticker</h2>\n<p>宠物床不一定要全都毛茸茸的才行，比利时设计师 Geerke Sticker 所使用的素材或许是最特殊的那一个：碗状的床由超高性能混凝土（UHPC）制成，通过三根纤细的木质床腿相连，看上去很像是小动物们栖息的洞穴。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111048HTWJfo2sG8qnhKNg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111049KjMXC8DhFtfUcwT1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111049ThDVieL9QWfSKUsN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111050xZrmhAoqK5WBFUsy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111050QFLRwCMTxZ8DjhSi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Furbo by Tomofun</h2>\n<p>为了了解家中狗狗的情况，一些上班族会选择使用摄像头远程监视，台湾的 Tomofun 以此为基础推出了一款可以丢零食的智能摄影机 Furbo，让你即使不在家也可以和狗狗互动。Furbo 使用起来也并不难：只需要下载好配套的手机应用然后将零食添加进机器中就可以使用了。一旦你准备抛送食物，Furbo 上的指示灯会点亮并且发出警报，通过一段时间的训练，狗狗就会立刻知道你打算用它和自己进行互动。为了安全，设计团队特地使用了工业强度的 3M 黏合剂，保证它不会被狗狗撞倒。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/furbo-world-s-first-treat-tossing-dog-camera#/\">链接</a>参与 Furbo 的众筹，最低售价为 119 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021110518FRlax5UZwtzCMIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5516129\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021110516M4BGE0l5p2Q7Rsn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111052Vcl5WY3BLDxk4i8y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7016129\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021110523KE2IhPQbapucBm7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70322581\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111053ZfTBRsxrEo6aJelG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70483871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702111053u09jSlrDVhT2Re5w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}